The next game's heroine is planned to be a
girl who is not our game's first long-
haired character.

I'm still in the stage of imagination, but
I'm fantasizing about a story where the
heroine is the protagonist's older
childhood friend, and they, along with
their mischievous friend (a virgin),
visit a southern island together...

The announcement regarding the next work
will be made on ci-en once the scenario
is somewhat finalized and the character
design for the heroine is completed.

......And finally, thank you very much for
playing until the end! There were twists
and turns along the way, but we were
able to safely deliver it to everyone,
and I am relieved.

Well then, it's a short greeting but... see
you later!
